title: Crypto Boosters Attack SEC For 'Manipulating' BTC Market After ETF Tweet
description: Lawmakers and crypto boosters are asking questions about how the SEC's X (formerly Twitter) account was compromised, leading to a bogus tweet on Tuesday.

title: SEC Twitter account hacked, false Bitcoin ETF approval tweet sends prices swinging
description: SEC Twitter hacked, fraudulent Bitcoin ETF approval tweet caused price swings.
